{"tid":2111163,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"事主庭上堅稱沒被打 「批肘」之說出於警員 男生脫普通襲擊罪","createTime":"2020-07-16T11:02:07.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-16T12:36:06.000Z","uid":240362,"like":25,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":22,"replies":[{"pid":"e954fb4f2efef4234ef28f71df3a4d38379e128d","tid":2111163,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-16T11:02:07.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200716/X6VJAKDSLQGZQCKPTJN6YMC4EQ/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200716%2FX6VJAKDSLQGZQCKPTJN6YMC4EQ%2F&d=q%2BUwj3SihaKoadPXZHTFaf7c%2B9HD3JYLAdxAiSxEDXo%3D&h=6fd921f5\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200716%2FX6VJAKDSLQGZQCKPTJN6YMC4EQ%2F&h=84c8a47c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200716/X6VJAKDSLQGZQCKPTJN6YMC4EQ/</a><br />\n<br />\n去年10月18日網民在五區進行快閃示威活動，其間現年19歲男生在牛頭角玉蓮臺疑因不滿被中年漢拍攝大頭照，雙方初則口角繼而動武。有途人勸交，從後箍著男生，最終雙雙倒地。男生被指向勸交途人「批肘」，遭控以普通襲擊罪，案件今在觀塘裁判法院開審。不過，事主出庭作供卻稱，男生沒有襲擊他，只因力不從心才會倒地。<strong><span class=\"red\">他曾婉拒錄口供，惟警員卻堅持稱「過程一定要清楚啲，睇吓係咪激進分子」。至於書面供詞上「批肘」之說，只是當時警員向他提議而寫下。案中另一證人證供亦類似，稱看不到「批肘」動作</span></strong>，裁判官梁少玲最終裁定案件表面證供不成立，被告脫普通襲擊罪。"},{"pid":"94f17fd7d76ef63ecd20244842c0baf93675459f","tid":2111163,"uid":219010,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-16T11:02:26.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/math.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8a92a081e8df9da4cd88f721140b7c78cb068317","tid":2111163,"uid":240362,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"94f17fd7d76ef63ecd20244842c0baf93675459f","tid":2111163,"uid":219010,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-16T11:02:26.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/math.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-16T11:02:50.000Z","msg":"警員<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\